'''''Ubwato n'Inyanja''''' ( [[Igiporutigali|Igiporutugali:]] '''''O Navio eo Mar''''' ) ni Filime ya documentaire ya 2019 yanditswe na Lara Sousa, iyobowe na Lara Sousa na Everlane Moraes kandi yakozwe na Lara Sousa na Matheus Mello. <ref name="Sand">https://sandtonchronicle.co.za/lnn/1141451/31-film-projects-across-africa-selected-to-pitch-at-durban-filmmarts-finance-forum</ref> <ref name="Tal">https://www.berlinale-talents.de/bt/project/profile/235307</ref>

== Umusaruro ==
firime yafotowe kandi ikorerwa muri [[Burezile|Berezile]], [[Mozambike|Mozambique]], [[Porutigali|Porutugali]] na [[Esipanye|Espagne]] namasosiyete akora: La Selva, Mosic, Laranjeira Filmes na Kinotop Filmes. Imiterere ya firime iri mumabara, Digital / Digital 5.1, Imiterere ya Dolby Stereo. Umusaruro uracyatezwa imbere. 

== Umugambi / Icegeranyo ==
Icyemezo cyafashwe na Everlane na Lara bo muri [[Burezile|Berezile]] na [[Mozambike|Mozambique]], bombi bakaba ari abakora amafilime y’abirabura, kugira ngo berekane indorerwamo bazenguruka igihugu cyabo mu buryo bwambukiranya imipaka, hanyuma bareba filime za buri wese kugira ngo bamenye imico yazimiye mu biranga umwirondoro wabo kumpande zombi kugirango wuzuze icyuho cyabuze. <ref>http://miradasdoc.com/mdoc2019/portfolio_page/o-navio-e-o-mar/?lang=en</ref> 

== Kwakira ==
Iyi filime yatoranijwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya 11 rya Durban (DIFF 2020) ryabaye hagati ya 10 na 20 Nzeri, kuri interineti, hamwe n’izindi filime zigera kuri 30 nka imwe mu mishinga y’Ihuriro ry’Imari. <ref>http://africultures.com/evenements/?no=49687</ref> <ref>https://ladima.africa/durban-filmmart-institute-announces-2020-durban-filmmart-finance-forum-projects/</ref>  <ref>http://www.durbanfilmmart.co.za/DFM-Projects</ref>

== Ibihembo ==
Iyi filime yatsindiye kandi muri Durban FilmMart ya 2020, Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime Amashusho Amsterdam (IDFA) Igihembo [[Ubuholandi|cy’Ubuholandi]] . <ref name="ONavio">https://m.bizcommunity.com/Article/196/482/208260.html</ref> <ref>https://www.idfa.nl/en/info/project-award-winners-at-idfa-2020</ref>

